snippet.title: Johnny Depp Gets REVENGE On Amber Heard! HUGE WIN For Johnny Depp!
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp has finally gotten some revenge on Amber Heard as Depp gets huge win over Heard. Every time we get new info on the Johnny Depp vs. Amber Heard situation, Amber Heard seems like a worse and worse person. But still Johnny Depp gets fired from WB, and Amber Heard lands Aquaman 2.
